data.text:
SOUTH PLAINFIELD POLICE DEPARTMENT

A Law Enforcement Agency, consisting of 58 sworn Officers, 10 full-time 9-1-1 Telecommunication Operators, and 4 civilian support staff members. It is the goal of the Police Department to provide the highest quality law enforcement services to residents and visitors alike. We strive to respond to community concerns and continuously seek input from the community.
